                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-486" type="given" value="MARGARET"></interp>MARGARET DRISCOLL</persName>
                  </hi>. About one o'clock that night the prisoner came to my house and slept with me—he left this watch with me for two nights.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was the worse for liquor; I did not know I had taken the watch out of the house; I found I had it; I gave it her, and said I would redeem it on Monday.</p>
